# 🧑‍💻 Sayed El-Sayed | Portfolio Website

> A modern and responsive **portfolio website** built using **Next.js**, **TypeScript**, and **Tailwind CSS** to showcase my skills, projects, and development journey as a Front-End Developer.

🌐 **Live Demo**: https://portfolio-alpha-beige-530yawe3ff.vercel.app/
---

## ✨ Overview

This is a personal portfolio website that represents who I am as a developer. It includes multiple sections such as:

- 🔝 Hero Section (brief intro)
- 🧠 Skills Section
- 🧩 Problem-Solving Showcase
- 📁 Projects Section
- 📈 Progress Log (my growth over time)
- 📬 Contact Section
- 🔻 Footer

All sections are modular and easy to maintain thanks to the component-based structure of React.

---

## 🔧 Tech Stack

| Tech               | Description                          |
|--------------------|--------------------------------------|
| **Next.js 13+**    | React Framework with App Router      |
| **TypeScript**     | Static typing for better structure   |
| **Tailwind CSS**   | Utility-first CSS framework          |
| **Vercel**         | Hosting and deployment               |
| **Git + GitHub**   | Version control                      |

---

## 📁 Project Structure

portfolio/
│
├── app/ # App routing system
│ ├── layout.tsx # Root layout
│ └── page.tsx # Homepage layout using sections
│
├── components/ # All UI components
│ ├── Header.tsx
│ ├── HeroSection.tsx
│ ├── SkillsSection.tsx
│ ├── ProblemSolverSection.tsx
│ ├── ProjectsSection.tsx
│ ├── ProgressLogSection.tsx
│ ├── ContactSection.tsx
│ └── Footer.tsx
│
├── styles/ # Global styles
├── public/ # Static assets
├── hooks/ # (Reserved for custom hooks)
├── lib/ # (Optional for utilities or helpers)
│
├── tailwind.config.ts # Tailwind config
├── tsconfig.json # TypeScript config
├── package.json # NPM metadata and scripts
└── next.config.mjs # Next.js configuration
